      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "An interview was given out by\nMayor Pratt today boosting the\nmeeting Friday night for the selec-\nton of an official committee to\nframe a new city charter. The\nmayor says that he Is much pleased\nwith the calling of the meeting and\nhopes that all friends of the COM\nmission form of government will\nturn out.\n\n\nHe commends the committee in\ncharge of the commission plan for\nthe zeal that 1t has shown and says\nthat a large meeting should be held\nFriday night to demonstrate that\nthe public is appreciative Of the la\nbors of the committee."
    }
